{"tid":1607421,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【英國戰線】繼929五大城市集會，十一英國又有突發行動鳥！賀佢老母！","createTime":"2019-09-30T22:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T17:49:18.000Z","uid":108502,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ac977e95ec7b5f934d08b6248a3859f07e17eab6","tid":1607421,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:26:46.000Z","msg":"Edinburgh:<br />\n10月1國殤日<br />\n活動日間: 1-2pm and 6-7pm<br />\n活動地點: Central campus<br />\n集合時間: 12:30pm<br />\n集合地點: Near Summerhall (pm for details)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">內容: full gear行campus</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLondon:<br />\n10月1 國殤日<br />\n集合時間: 4:45pm (set野, come at 16:45 to help set up stuff if you can!)<br />\n活動時間: 5:00pm-7:00/8:00pm<br />\n集合地點: Piccadilly Circus<br />\nDress code: BLACK BLOC to cover your entire face<br />\n<br />\nBirmingham:<br />\n10月1 國殤日<br />\n集合時間: 4:30pm<br />\n集合地點: Birmingham new street wasabi<br />\n集會時間: 5:00pm-7:00pm<br />\n集會地點: Central Birmingham<br />\n<br />\nManchester:<br />\n10月1 國殤日<br />\n集合時間: 3pm <br />\n集合地點: Manchester University Place <br />\n集會時間: 4pm-7pm (TBC)<br />\n集會地點: University Place (TBC)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大致內容 (London / Birmingham/ Manchester):<br />\n1. 街站派leaflets<br />\n2. 唱願榮光+do u hear the people sing<br />\n3. 盡量邀請外國人加入我哋<br />\n4. 介紹有template，請背好<br />\n5. 有冇有音樂天賦嘅人可以帶樂器齋for願榮光<br />\n6. 有冇人識剪片<br />\n7. 有gear要好小心安全<br />\n8. 當有途人支持時，希望大家會一齊鞠躬多謝<br />\n9. 唔好同警察講我哋而家散啦之類<br />\n由於我哋嘅文宣同物資都係手足自己預備嘅，大家都係學生，則唔係大富大貴，所以希望大家唔好抱住過嚟會有嘢攞嘅概況，同時則想大家都幫下手print文宣同自備物資</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請加入TG公海：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/C5voK1egJWHZDjxFqNnzDw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FC5voK1egJWHZDjxFqNnzDw&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdcjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=ae2f74b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/C5voK1egJWHZDjxFqNnzDw</a><br />\n*為免被bot自動篩走 請於入谷後回答簡單數學題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"> 有興趣幫手嘅巴絲請先入公海谷留言 到時admin會加你入行動谷 目前唔同城市/region都有谷！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"6bc380828bd751f0bdd36183510f1ed532405b9b","tid":1607421,"uid":266212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:27:50.000Z","msg":"p牌一推"},{"pid":"a4d41bea7c0f67c2bf448dc53f0e5de7ebff69f3","tid":1607421,"uid":177944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e57e39892aab738c5750d5e5f3f37b30274efa3","tid":1607421,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1d11fa9f3e65a5a8c0bb7fc2a099b4c9eef6cf","tid":1607421,"uid":161735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:35:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e0806586946c586028820590afa112d96271258","tid":1607421,"uid":130539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:35:30.000Z","msg":"有冇其他大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學校上足全日出唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d6f68aec54b8c7d6b89ec6e0730c43c54b8102","tid":1607421,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9a8298e0a3a608e03c2bbaf8b982276b245eee","tid":1607421,"uid":318750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T22:36:19.000Z","msg":"PUSHHHHHH"},{"pid":"f7d268d58868a8f3cf3576c59b26cf64fba4382c","tid":1607421,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e0806586946c58602